labels.label: For each row returned, set an "_id" so we can do Upsert when ingesting data
Find the latest "last_change" date in ES
Query the db for anything with a change later than the latest"last_change"

entry.value: SELECT concat(investigations.subject_entity_uid, ',', investigations.participation_type_cd, ',', investigations.act_uid, ',', investigations.act_id_seq) id, ( SELECT Max(v) FROM ( VALUES(person_last_chg_time), (public_health_case_last_chg_time), (act_id_last_chg_time), (notification_last_chg_time), (participation_last_chg_time)) AS value (v)) AS last_change, investigations.* FROM ( SELECT public_health_case.program_jurisdiction_oid program_jurisdiction_oid, public_health_case.case_type_cd case_type_cd, act.mood_cd mood_cd, public_health_case.cd_desc_txt cd_desc_txt, public_health_case.prog_area_cd prog_area_cd, public_health_case.jurisdiction_cd jurisdiction_cd, public_health_case.pregnant_ind_cd pregnant_ind_cd, act_id.act_id_seq act_id_seq, act_id.root_extension_txt root_extension_txt, act_id.type_cd act_id_type_cd, act_id.last_chg_time act_id_last_chg_time, public_health_case.local_id public_health_case_local_id, notification.local_id notification_local_id, public_health_case.rpt_form_cmplt_time rpt_form_cmplt_time, public_health_case.activity_to_time activity_to_time, public_health_case.add_time add_time, public_health_case.activity_from_time activity_from_time, public_health_case.last_chg_time public_health_case_last_chg_time, notification.add_time notification_add_time, public_health_case.add_user_id add_user_id, public_health_case.last_chg_user_id last_chg_user_id, participation.act_uid act_uid, participation.type_cd participation_type_cd, participation.subject_entity_uid subject_entity_uid, participation.last_chg_time participation_last_chg_time, person.last_chg_time person_last_chg_time, person.cd person_cd, person.record_status_cd person_record_status_cd, public_health_case.investigation_status_cd investigation_status_cd, public_health_case.outbreak_name outbreak_name, public_health_case.case_class_cd class_cd, notification.record_status_cd notification_record_status_cd, notification.last_chg_time notification_last_chg_time, public_health_case.curr_process_state_cd curr_process_state_cd FROM dbo.public_health_case public_health_case LEFT JOIN dbo.notification notification ON (public_health_case.public_health_case_uid = notification.notification_uid) JOIN dbo.act_id act_id ON (public_health_case.public_health_case_uid = act_id.act_uid) JOIN dbo.participation participation ON (public_health_case.public_health_case_uid = participation.act_uid) JOIN dbo.person person ON (participation.subject_entity_uid = person.person_uid) JOIN dbo.act act ON public_health_case.public_health_case_uid = act.act_uid) AS investigations WHERE ( SELECT Max(v) FROM ( VALUES(person_last_chg_time), (public_health_case_last_chg_time), (act_id_last_chg_time), (notification_last_chg_time), (participation_last_chg_time)) AS value (v)) > '${last_change}' ORDER BY last_change ASC;
